{
  "stem": "5470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got to know, of course, right away the organization in the camp as well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Germans got hold of Camp Westerbork on the 1st of July, 1942.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they never were there at the particular time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Actually, they took over the camp, not any earlier than on the 1st of January 1943.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And before that time, there was only someone there as a contact person between the Dutch government and the German government, because the full camps was, by that time, under control of the Dutch government and the Department of Justice.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the department.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was appointed then by the Department of Justice as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the day thereafter, the contact person got to know that there was a new person in the camp appointed, and he complained about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who did the appointment?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I couldn't leave the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a prisoner in the camp too for about four or five weeks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Couldn't leave the camp until they found out how my appointment came into being.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there I was doing nothing and said, yeah, what's going to happen now?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the underground was-- our group was trying to find out if there was other possibilities to keep me there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, because of the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they knew, already, more.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because of the fact that I couldn't do anything at all and couldn't move in the office with [INAUDIBLE] and had to stay outside, the only thing what they could do was move into the camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because in the camp itself, it was completely free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there I got the chance of my life to get to know the whole organization, the people there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
